dynGuiComponents.name: android.widget.TextView
dynGuiComponents.text: Welcome to Fast N Fitness! This application is a quick and simple way to record your program and follow your progression and the evolution of your body.

dynGuiComponents.name: android.widget.TextView
dynGuiComponents.text: Write the name of the exercise and the details, and it will be created automatically. You can find it back easily in the list.

dynGuiComponents.name: android.widget.TextView
dynGuiComponents.text: No exercises are pre-created. You create your own exercises simply depending on the name of the machine you have in your fitness place / location.

dynGuiComponents.name: android.widget.TextView
dynGuiComponents.text: Join the community and let's build the best fitness app together! Visit us at https://github.com/brodeurlv/fastnfitness
